reviewText: Reminds me of the very old days when I actually saw her on  TV and attended her conventions. Nothing else compares to what she offered spiritually to those who came to see her. I am thrilled to have an entire set of DVDs to reminisce about the 'good old days'. BTW, if you have questions about her abilities, talents and gifts - I was there and confirm that yes, she is everything she represents on the DVDs. No drama, no script, no acting. Pure, simple spirit at work.

Excellent... brought me back to her wonderful teaching and ministering "miracle" services..
would greatly recommend
Clayton
